products.name: CASH Connect Account
products.description: The CASH Connect Account is an at call transaction account designed to allow customers the flexibility of accessing their funds at any time while offering a standard variable base rate interest. The CASH Connect Account is a ?transaction account? that can be linked to the eWRAP Investments Account, or held as a standalone at call transaction account. When linked to a eWRAP Investment Account, the CASH Connect Account is used to settle managed fund and equity trades, as well as facilitate transactions and consequent cash movements including the receipt of deposits and payment of fees.

products.name: eCASH Account
products.description: The eCASH Account is an electronic style at call transaction account designed to allow customers the flexibility of accessing their funds at any time while offering a  variable interest rate. The eCASH  Account is the default ?transaction account? that can be linked to the eWRAP Investments Account, or held as a standalone at call transaction account. When linked to a eWRAP Investment Account, the eCASH  Account is used to settle managed fund and equity trades, as well as facilitate transactions and consequent cash movements including the receipt of deposits and payment of fees.

products.name: Hire Purchase
products.description: A Commercial Hire Purchase is an agreement for the Bank to purchase an asset at the customer's request.  The Bank gives the customer possession and use of the asset in return for regular repayments.  Once fully repaid ownership in the asset is transferred to the customer.

products.description: A Goods Loan is a fixed rate loan used to finance the purchase of eligible new or used vehicles or equipment. The customer purchases and owns the asset and gives the Bank security over it.
